<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>À propos de GoldInvest</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.19/dist/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
    <style>
        /* Styles cohérents avec index.ejs */
        .hero {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f59e0b 0%, #d97706 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 4rem 0;
        }

        .glass {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            padding: 4rem 0;
        }

        .content-wrapper {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 1rem;
        }

        .section-title {
            color: #1e293b;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .feature-card {
            background: white;
            padding: 2rem;
            border-radius: 1rem;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.1), 0 2px 4px -2px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.1);
            border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .feature-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.1), 0 4px 6px -4px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.1);
            border-color: #d1d5db;
        }

        .number-circle {
            width: 60px;
            height: 60px;
            background: #f59e0b;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: white;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f59e0b 0%, #fbbf24 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            border-radius: 0.5rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fbbf24 0%, #f59e0b 100%);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.1), 0 2px 4px -2px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.1);
        }

        .gold-image {
            background-image: url('/assets/img/gold_invest.jpeg');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            height: 300px;
            border-radius: 1rem;
            margin: 2rem 0;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.1), 0 2px 4px -2px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.1);
        }

        footer {
            background: #1e293b;
            color: white;
            padding: 3rem 0;
        }

        footer a {
            color: white;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }

        footer a:hover {
            color: #f59e0b;
        }

        /* Amélioration de la lisibilité du texte */
        .glass p {
            color: #1e293b;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .glass h2 {
            color: #1e293b;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .glass h3 {
            color: #1e293b;
            margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
        }

        .glass .text-gray-600 {
            color: #4b5563;
        }

        .glass .text-gray-700 {
            color: #374151;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .hero {
                padding: 3rem 0;
            }

            .section-title {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }

            .feature-card {
                padding: 1.5rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="font-inter bg-gray-50">
    <nav class="bg-transparent p-4">
        <div class="container mx-auto flex justify-between items-center">
            <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">
                <span class="text-yellow-400">Gold</span>Invest
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
                <a href="/" class="text-white hover:text-yellow-400">Accueil</a>
                <a href="/contact" class="text-white hover:text-yellow-400">Contact</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <section class="hero">
        <div class="content-wrapper text-center">
            <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6">
                À propos de GoldInvest
            </h1>
            <p class="text-xl mb-8">
                Découvrez notre plateforme d'investissement moderne et sécurisée
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="glass">
        <div class="content-wrapper">
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
                <div>
                    <h2 class="section-title">Notre Mission</h2>
                    <p class="mb-6 text-gray-700">
                        Chez GoldInvest, notre mission est de démocratiser l'investissement 
                        dans l'or numérique en offrant une plateforme sécurisée et intuitive.
                    </p>
                    <div class="space-y-6">
                        <div class="feature-card">
                            <div class="number-circle">1</div>
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Sécurité</h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-600">Transactions sécurisées via la blockchain TRON</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="feature-card">
                            <div class="number-circle">2</div>
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Transparence</h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-600">Un suivi en temps réel de vos investissements</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="feature-card">
                            <div class="number-circle">3</div>
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Simplicité</h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-600">Interface utilisateur intuitive et accessible</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h2 class="section-title">Notre Histoire</h2>
                    <p class="mb-6 text-gray-700">
                        Fondée en 2025, GoldInvest a été créée par des experts en finance 
                        et en technologie blockchain. Notre objectif est de révolutionner 
                        l'industrie de l'investissement en rendant l'or numérique accessible 
                        à tous.
                    </p>
                    <div class="space-y-6">
                        <div class="feature-card">
                            <div class="number-circle">2025</div>
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Lancement</h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-600">Lancement officiel de la plateforme</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="feature-card">
                            <div class="number-circle">Q2</div>
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Expansion</h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-600">Extension de nos services à l'international</p>
                        <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="bg-transparent text-white py-8">
        <div class="container mx-auto">
            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center">
                <div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">GoldInvest</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-400"> 2025 GoldInvest. Tous droits réservés.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="flex space-x-4 mt-4 md:mt-0">
                    <a href="/" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white">Accueil</a>
                    <a href="/contact" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white">Contact</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
